<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verifikasi Voucher - Broco Smart Care</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { background: #f0f2f5; display: flex; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
    .voucher-card { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
    .verified-badge { background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 50px; display: inline-block; }
    .header-bar { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a237e, #283593); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header-bar img { height: 40px; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card voucher-card shadow">
      <div class="header-bar">
        <img src="https://broco-care.tech/images/logo.png" alt="Broco">
        <h4 class="mt-2 mb-0">Verifikasi Voucher Garansi</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <% if (!v) { %>
          <div class="text-center py-5">
            <div class="display-1 text-danger mb-3"><i class="bi bi-x-octagon-fill"></i></div>
            <h5 class="text-danger">Voucher Tidak Valid</h5>
            <p class="text-muted">Voucher tidak ditemukan atau sudah tidak berlaku.</p>
            <p class="small text-muted">Hubungi PT. Broco Retail Solution untuk informasi lebih lanjut.</p>
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <% if (v.status === 'active') { %>
              <span class="verified-badge"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-1"></i> VOUCHER AKTIF</span>
            <% } else { %>
              <span class="badge bg-secondary fs-6 p-2">VOUCHER TIDAK AKTIF</span>
            <% } %>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="border-bottom pb-2 mb-3">
              <small class="text-muted">No. Voucher</small>
              <div class="fw-bold fs-5"><%= v.voucher_no %></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <table class="table table-sm table-borderless">
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary" style="width:140px;">Nama Konsumen</td>
              <td class="fw-semibold"><%= v.customer_name %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">No. HP</td>
              <td><%= v.customer_hp || '-' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">Produk</td>
              <td><%= v.product_name || '-' %> <%= v.product_type ? '('+v.product_type+')' : '' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">Serial Number</td>
              <td><%= v.serial_number || '-' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">Keluhan</td>
              <td><%= v.keluhan || '-' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">Keputusan</td>
              <td><span class="badge bg-info"><%= v.decision %></span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">Tanggal Dibuat</td>
              <td><%= v.created_at %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-secondary">Berlaku s/d</td>
              <td><%= v.expired_at || '-' %></td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <div class="alert alert-info small mt-3">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
            Voucher ini adalah bukti resmi dari PT. Broco Retail Solution. Untuk pertanyaan lebih lanjut, hubungi Customer Service kami.
          </div>

          <div class="text-center text-muted small mt-4">
            PT. Broco Retail Solution &copy; 2026
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
